                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The 351st meeting of the General Assembly’s First Committee took place on October
                    3 from 3 to 5:45 p. m.; for the record, see U.N. document A/C.1/SR.351. The
                    debate on the eight-power and five-power draft resolutions continued, but no
                    voting took place.</p>
            </div>
